@node Registrazione
@title " Registration and Limits "

The Demo version is obviously limited:
- Window Delay for 1 second on any human actions
- Displacement of troops not usable

You  may like have this version?  You must be a registered user:  if you be
an  registered  user  you  will  have  a good price for the future upgrades
versions.   The price for the registration is 15.000 Italian £.  This money
must  be  sended with a postal order for the autor.  You must send also the
@{"  Module  of  registration " link Modulo} complete with your data (name,
address,  country,  etc.).   You must not send money in other modes (can do
not arrive).  At the reception of the money (and the module with your data)
I will send you the last version completes of the program.

@endnode
