@node Azioni
@title " Use of file azioni.dat "

For  to  eliminate  bugs,  each actions  come  recorded  in  a  file  named
"azioni.dat"  in  the  directory  program.  If you note problems, after the
game  copy this file non another directory or floppy and rename it and send
me  at  this  e-mail  address  denni@mbox.tec.it  or send me your floppy.

@endnode
